Users who have downloaded the app simply find the images in magazines or online, then hold their smartphone with the app open over the code found on the image.

The model's clothes will instantly disappear - leaving her in the underwear (and, cleverly, details on where to buy it).

The Wonderbra Decoder app is part of the brand's new marketing campaign that hopes to provide users with a more interactive experience.

App users can scan multiple dressed images of 
Adriana to reveal the different Wonderbra behind her look and view a 
gallery of recommended Wonderbras for different outfits, from daywear to
 special occasions.

